"{\"uid\": \"newstodaynet.com-2024-08-07-modis-emotional-message-after-vinesh-phogats-disqualification-from-paris-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"News Today | First with the news  News Today | First with the news          In a heartfelt message, Prime Minister Narendra Modi expressed his deep disappointment and unwavering support for Vinesh Phogat.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 204, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 115, \"end\": 128, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Narendra_Modi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Narendra Modi\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Narendra_Modi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Narendra_Modi\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Taking to social media platform X, Prime Minister Modi posted a message that resonated with millions of Indians who had been rooting for Vinesh.\", \"from\": 206, \"to\": 350, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 256, \"end\": 260, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Narendra_Modi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.307715448294895e-16, \"text\": \"Modi\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Narendra_Modi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Narendra_Modi\"}, {\"begin\": 310, \"end\": 317, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\", \"score\": 0.9997970336341456, \"rank\": 0.00010383887950764891, \"text\": \"Indians\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\"}, {\"begin\": 343, \"end\": 349, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vinesh\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Vinesh, you are a champion among champions!\", \"from\": 351, \"to\": 395, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You are India's pride and an inspiration for each and every Indian.\", \"from\": 396, \"to\": 463, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 404, \"end\": 409, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 0.9999997005859762, \"rank\": 1.4073858485440002e-07, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}, {\"begin\": 456, \"end\": 462, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 0.9523859308167176, \"rank\": 0.04999140638839226, \"text\": \"Indian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Today's setback hurts.\", \"from\": 464, \"to\": 486, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I wish words could express the sense of despair that I am experiencing.\", \"from\": 487, \"to\": 558, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"At the same time, I know that you epitomise resilience.\", \"from\": 559, \"to\": 614, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It has always been your nature to take challenges head on.\", \"from\": 615, \"to\": 673, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Come back stronger!\", \"from\": 674, \"to\": 693, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are all rooting for you,\\\" the Prime Minister wrote, reflecting the collective sorrow and admiration of the nation.\", \"from\": 694, \"to\": 811, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"According to sources, Prime Minister Modi also reached out to PT Usha, veteran athlete and President of the Indian Olympics Association (IOA), to discuss the situation.\", \"from\": 813, \"to\": 981, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 850, \"end\": 854, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Narendra_Modi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.307715448294895e-16, \"text\": \"Modi\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Narendra_Modi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Narendra_Modi\"}, {\"begin\": 875, \"end\": 882, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/P._T._Usha\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"PT Usha\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/P._T._Usha\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/P._T._Usha\"}, {\"begin\": 921, \"end\": 927, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 0.9523859308167176, \"rank\": 0.04999140638839226, \"text\": \"Indian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He urged the IOA chief to explore all possible options for India and Vinesh Phogat, emphasizing the importance of registering India's strong protest against the disqualification.\", \"from\": 982, \"to\": 1160, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 995, \"end\": 998, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_Olympic_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"IOA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_Olympic_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_Olympic_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 1041, \"end\": 1046, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 0.9999997005859762, \"rank\": 1.4073858485440002e-07, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}, {\"begin\": 1051, \"end\": 1064, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vinesh Phogat\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\"}, {\"begin\": 1108, \"end\": 1113, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 0.9999997005859762, \"rank\": 1.4073858485440002e-07, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}]}]}"